jQuery Tag Box Widget Plugin
Khalid Al-Kooheji (http://kkdev.blogspot.com)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Description:

converts a list into a text box where a user can enter some tags and moves 
around the tags or deletes them.
tags are entered into the list by pressing space/enter.

jquery.tagbox.js : javascript source code
tagbox.css : basic styling

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Usage :

to create simply :
	$('ul').tagbox();

to get the tags as an array
	var listOfTags = $('ul').tagbox('getTagList');

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Options:

suggestionsSource: if not null will be passed to jqueryui autocomplete plugin and 
		   will allow suggestion dropdown menu as you type a new tag , default value : null

allowDuplicates: allow duplicate tag entries , default value : false

tagList: array of initial tags to be added , default value : null

formatter: a function to format the item element default value : function (val) {  return '<span>' + val + '</span>';   }

